{"number":5,"verseCount":26,"verses":[[1,[["Stand",["study-note-ref","a",[["Philip. 4:1 (1–7)","nt/philip/4.1"],"."]]]," fast therefore in the ",["liberty",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Liberty","tg/liberty"],"."]]]," wherewith Christ hath made us ",["free",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 2:26 (26–27)","bofm/2-ne/2.26"],"; ",["Mosiah 5:8","bofm/mosiah/5.8"],"; ",["Alma 61:9 (9, 21)","bofm/alma/61.9"],"."]]],", and be not ",["entangled",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 88:86","dc-testament/dc/88.86"],"."]]]," again with the yoke of ",["bondage",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Bondage, Spiritual","tg/bondage-spiritual"],"; ",["Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]],"."]],[2,["Behold, I Paul say unto you, that if ye be circumcised, Christ shall profit you nothing."]],[3,["For I testify again to every man that is ",["circumcised",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 2:25","nt/rom/2.25"],"."]]],", that he is a debtor to do the whole law."]],[4,["Christ is become of no effect unto you, whosoever of you are justified by the ",["law",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Law of Moses","tg/law-of-moses"],"."]]],"; ye are fallen from ",["grace",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]],"."]],[5,["For we through the Spirit wait for the hope of righteousness by ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rom. 5:2 (1–5)","nt/rom/5.2"],"; ",["1 Pet. 1:21 (21–22)","nt/1-pet/1.21"],"."]]],"."]],[6,["For in Jesus Christ neither ",["circumcision",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Circumcision","tg/circumcision"],"."]]]," ",["availeth any thing",["study-note-ref","b",["GR has any power, validity, service."]]],", nor uncircumcision; but ",["faith",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]]," which worketh by ",["love",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Love","tg/love"],"."]]],"."]],[7,["Ye did run well; who did hinder you that ye should not ",["obey",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Disobedience","tg/disobedience"],"."]]]," the truth?"]],[8,["This persuasion ",["cometh",["clarity-word"]]," not of him that calleth y